  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1387570/extras/c31dac4ceb38fde9506825afe9c9ea51.avif?t=1721122160\" width=600 height=150 /></span><br><br>Attempt the role of an Orbitect in this roguelite space construction game (with tower defence elements)!  Your job is simple; space is a dirty place, time to turn that waste into wealth.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> <strong>Destroy increasingly challenging waves </strong> of space debris as it hurtles across the galaxy! Can you survive until wave 100?<br><br></li><li> <strong>Construct free-form space stations </strong> using the resources you’ve harvested from the debris.<br><br></li><li> <strong>Weapons fire automatically</strong> allowing you to focus on your build.<br><br></li><li> <strong>Unlock new weapons and defence options</strong> during a run and upgrade them to become unstoppable.<br><br></li><li> <strong>Purchase permanent boosts</strong> to improve your next run - even in defeat, there’s something to be gained.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1387570/extras/2e873722a39f83430dbcaa29fd1c2ecb.poster.avif?t=1721122160\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1387570/extras/2e873722a39f83430dbcaa29fd1c2ecb.webm?t=1721122160\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1387570/extras/2e873722a39f83430dbcaa29fd1c2ecb.mp4?t=1721122160\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1387570/extras/cd31614d6aefab12dd85ef500c0c3536.poster.avif?t=1721122160\" width=600 height=336 ><source s